BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 142.07999999999998 610 Td (UNDERSTANDING INSOMNIA) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 40 600 m 392 600 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 580 Td (CBT-I \(Cognitive Behavioral Therapy for Insomnia\) is the #1) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 565 Td (recommended treatment for chronic insomnia - even above medication.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 550 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 535 Td (WHY CBT-I WORKS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 520 Td (- Addresses the ROOT CAUSES of insomnia, not just symptoms) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 505 Td (- Effects last long after treatment \(unlike sleeping pills\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 490 Td (- No side effects, no dependency) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 475 Td (- Recommended by the American Academy of Sleep Medicine) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 460 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 445 Td (THE 3P MODEL OF INSOMNIA:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 430 Td (Predisposing: You may be naturally lighter sleeper) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 415 Td (Precipitating: A stressful event triggered the insomnia) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 400 Td (Perpetuating: HABITS you developed that now maintain it) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 385 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 370 Td (COMMON PERPETUATING HABITS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 355 Td (- Going to bed too early \(lying awake builds anxiety\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 340 Td (- Staying in bed when not sleeping \(bed = awake place\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 325 Td (- Napping during the day \(reduces sleep drive\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 310 Td (- Clock watching \(increases frustration\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 295 Td (- Compensating \(caffeine, sleeping in on weekends\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 280 Td (- Worrying about sleep \(creates hyperarousal\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 265 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 250 Td (THIS WORKBOOK COVERS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 235 Td (1. Sleep diary \(track your actual patterns\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 220 Td (2. Sleep restriction \(counterintuitive but powerful\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 205 Td (3. Stimulus control \(retrain your brain about bed\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 190 Td (4. Cognitive restructuring \(stop worry about sleep\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 175 Td (5. Relaxation techniques) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 160 Td (6. Sleep hygiene optimization) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
