BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 445 Td (2. Only go to bed when sleepy \(not just tired\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 430 Td (   Sleepy = eyes heavy, head nodding, yawning) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 415 Td (   NOT: 'I should go to bed because it's late') Tj ET
