BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 125.52000000000001 610 Td (PROGRESSIVE MUSCLE RELAXATION) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 40 600 m 392 600 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 580 Td (Do this in bed when trying to sleep. Takes 10-15 minutes.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 565 Td (Tense each muscle group 5 seconds, release 15 seconds.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 550 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 535 Td (SEQUENCE \(go slowly through each\):) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 520 Td (1. Feet: Curl toes tightly... release) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 505 Td (2. Calves: Point toes toward face... release) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 490 Td (3. Thighs: Squeeze thighs together... release) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 475 Td (4. Buttocks: Clench... release) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 460 Td (5. Stomach: Pull belly button to spine... release) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 445 Td (6. Chest: Take deep breath, hold... release) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 430 Td (7. Hands: Make tight fists... release) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 415 Td (8. Arms: Flex biceps... release) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 400 Td (9. Shoulders: Shrug to ears... release) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 385 Td (10. Neck: Gently press head into pillow... release) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 370 Td (11. Face: Scrunch all facial muscles... release) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 355 Td (12. Whole body: Tense everything at once... release) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 340 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 325 Td (TIPS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 310 Td (- Focus on the CONTRAST between tense and relaxed) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 295 Td (- Breathe in while tensing, out while releasing) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 280 Td (- If your mind wanders, gently come back to the muscle) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 265 Td (- Don't worry about doing it 'perfectly') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 250 Td (- Practice daily, even on good sleep nights) Tj ET
