BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 122.4 610 Td (WHEN TO SEE A SLEEP SPECIALIST) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 40 600 m 392 600 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 580 Td (CBT-I works for most people, but see a doctor if:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 565 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 550 Td ([ ] You've tried CBT-I consistently for 6+ weeks with no help) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 535 Td ([ ] You snore loudly or have been told you stop breathing) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 520 Td ([ ] You have restless legs that prevent sleep) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 505 Td ([ ] You fall asleep uncontrollably during the day) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 490 Td ([ ] You have unusual behaviors during sleep \(acting out dreams\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 475 Td ([ ] Your insomnia started after a medication change) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 460 Td ([ ] You have significant depression or anxiety with insomnia) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 445 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 430 Td (POSSIBLE SLEEP DISORDERS TO RULE OUT:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 415 Td (- Sleep Apnea \(breathing stops during sleep\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 400 Td (- Restless Leg Syndrome \(irresistible urge to move legs\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 385 Td (- Narcolepsy \(excessive daytime sleepiness\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 370 Td (- Circadian Rhythm Disorders \(body clock misaligned\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 355 Td (- Parasomnias \(sleepwalking, sleep talking\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 340 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 325 Td (HOW TO FIND A SLEEP SPECIALIST:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 310 Td (- Ask your primary care doctor for a referral) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 295 Td (- Look for board-certified sleep medicine physicians) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 280 Td (- Check if CBT-I therapists are available in your area) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 265 Td (- Online CBT-I programs \(Insomnia Coach app is free\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 250 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 235 Td (REMEMBER:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 220 Td (You deserve good sleep. It's not a luxury. It's a) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 205 Td (fundamental health need. Keep working at it.) Tj ET

endstream
